Monsanto Chemical Company, a unit ofMonsanto Co &lt;MTC.N>, is to acquire the polyphenyls business ofRhone-Poulenc Chimie, a unit of Rhone-Poulenc &lt;RHON.PA>,Monsanto said in a statement issued from its Europeanheadquarters.    The statement did not disclose financial details.    Gustaaf Francx, general manager of Monsanto Chemical CoEurope-Africa, said the acquisition would help Monsanto toexpand its customer base for polyphenyls, which are used ascomponents for high temperature heat transfer fluids. Reuter&#3;